/* global window, OOo */

(function (w, d, o) {

  var OpinionLabInit = function () {

    /* PayPal custom variables */
    var opVars = typeof PAYPAL !== 'undefined' ? (typeof PAYPAL.opinionLabVars !== 'undefined' ? PAYPAL.opinionLabVars : '') : '',
      guid = opVars.guid,
      experimentId = opVars.experimentId,
      treatmentId = opVars.treatmentId,
      tealeafId = opVars.guid,
      rLogId = opVars.rLogId,
      fptiPagename = opVars.fptiPagename,
      fptiPageGroup = opVars.fptiPageGroup,
      countryCode = opVars.countryCode.toLowerCase(),
      langCode = opVars.languageCode.toLowerCase();

    /* Feedback object configuration */
    o.oo_feedback = new o.Ocode({
      referrerRewrite: w.location.protocol + '//' + w.location.hostname + '/' + countryCode + '/' + langCode + '/' + fptiPagename,
      legacyVariables: {
        vars: tealeafId,
        override: true
      },
      customVariables: {
        guid: guid,
        experimentId: experimentId,
        treatmentId: treatmentId,
        tealeafId: tealeafId,
        rLogId: rLogId,
        fptiPagename: fptiPagename,
        fptiPageGroup: fptiPageGroup,
        countryCode: countryCode,
        languageCode: langCode
      }
    });

    var sfLink = d.getElementById('siteFeedback');
    if (sfLink) {
      sfLink.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        var evt = e || w.event;
        o.oo_feedback.show(evt);
      });
    }

    if (opVars.showSitefbIcon) {
      var sfImg = d.createElement('img');
      sfImg.setAttribute('src', opVars.sitefb_plus_icon);
      sfImg.setAttribute('alt', '');
      sfLink.appendChild(sfImg);
    }
  };

  o.addEventListener(w, 'load', OpinionLabInit, false);
})(window, document, OOo);
